from\": 1488, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to to get the win, and give us the the chance to fight for the medal for Spain.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999764163260564, \"rank\": 2.3583664912643348e-05, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We could not keep going but I am going to try to keep this experience and try to forget this bad moment and focus on tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if his relationship will Nadal will remain strong after this tournament, four-time Grand Slam winner Alcaraz, whowon Wimbledon again last month, said: \\\"Yeah for sure.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1779, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6178373098432996e-28, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3108991360011638e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999513552106126, \"rank\": 4.8640168762838274e-05, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Wimbledon